  "title": "🚀🔥 NO EXPERIENCE NEEDED🔥🚀 Junior Marketing & Sales",
  "description": "<p>If sitting at a desk all day sounds like a nightmare…<br />If you prefer people > emails…<br />If you want skills you can actually use IRL 👀<br />…keep reading.</p><p>At <strong>Thrive Organisation</strong>, It’s hands-on, fast-paced, and very much <strong>learn-by-doing</strong> energy.</p><h3>💬 What You’ll Be Doing</h3><p>• Talking to people & representing brands (no NPC vibes pls)<br />• Communicating messages confidently & clearly<br />• Learning marketing & sales through real interactions<br />• Working with a fun, driven team that has your back</p><h3>💥 What You’ll Get</h3><p>• Coaching & guidance as you go (you won’t be thrown alone)<br />• Performance incentives, bonuses & recognition 💰<br />• Exposure to different campaigns & environments 🌍<br />• A positive, energetic culture (we celebrate wins loud)</p><h3>👀 This Is For You If…</h3><p>• You enjoy chatting OR want to stop being awkward 😭<br />• You’re at the <strong>early stage of your career</strong><br />• You’re open-minded, coachable, and down to try</p><p>✨ You don’t need confidence to start.<br />You build it here.</p><p>👉 Apply, come down, see how it works —<br />then decide if it’s your thing.</p>",
